Burnley host Arsenal at Turf Moor in the Premier League on Saturday . 
  Matt Taylor could make his return from a seven-and-a-half month injury lay-off for the Clarets . 
  Laurent Koscielny and Wojciech Szczesny face fitness tests for the Gunners . 
  Jack Wilshere and Santi Cazorla could also feature for Arsenal . 
  Burnley have won just one of their last seven Premier League games . 
 